Package org.eclipse.emf.compare.rcp.ui.internal.structuremergeviewer.filters.impl

Class TechnicalitiesFilter

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.emf.compare.rcp.ui.structuremergeviewer.filters.AbstractDifferenceFilter
org.eclipse.emf.compare.rcp.ui.internal.structuremergeviewer.filters.impl.TechnicalitiesFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDeactivableDiffFilter, IDifferenceFilter
public class TechnicalitiesFilter
extends AbstractDifferenceFilter

A filter used by default that rejects all 'technical' differences. The technical differences are the diffs that apply on empty MatchResources, on FeatureMap diffs, on identical elements and on pseudo-conflicts.

This filter aggregates the former 4 corresponding filters.
